	<div itemprop="text"><p>I turned of debug manually in the config file &#8211; now I get a message: </p>
<p>The domain mapping plugin only works if the site is installed in /. This is a limitation of how virtual servers work and is very difficult to work around.</p>
<p>If I delete the domain_mapping.php file the admin window comes up fine &#8211; but with no superadmin or sites configured.</p>
