<p>My biggest concern, before I push any buttons to move down the &#8220;Create a Network&#8221; path or install this MU Domain Mapping plugin, is that <strong>I cannot lose the existing URL structure</strong> in the current and mature PW site. Too much work has been done in SEO and too many external sites have link backs that the URL simply cannot change.</p>
<p>Do you have any advice or direction you can point me in?</p>
<p>Thanks @Otto</p>
