	<div itemprop="text"><p>Hello</p>
<p>I have created blogs for each country of where I have my online store, using one unique main installation of wordpress and then mapping my country domains.</p>
<p>So my blogs are:<br />
blog.countrydomain1.de<br />
blog.countrydomain2.es<br />
blog.countrydomain3.com.br</p>
<p>Could you let me know where is my SEO juice &#8220;going&#8221; with such configuration?<br />
